OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784913523
OL,3,CWhy euro notes are being redesigned -
OL,4,Cand how you can have a say
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Producer, Kieran
OL,7,FCarter
OL,9,FThe EU is redesigning its money, and
OL,10,Fdespite no longer being part of the
OL,11,Ftrading bloc - you can still have a
OL,12,Fsay in how the new notes will look.
OL,14,FThe European Central Bank (ECB) has
OL,15,Flaunched a consultation on a series of
OL,16,Fdesigns which could replace the notes
OL,17,Fcurrently available across euro-using
OL,18,FEU countries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/33
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784913523
OL,3,CWhy euro notes are being redesigned -
OL,4,Cand how you can have a say
OL,6,FThe potential designs feature notable
OL,7,FEuropean figures, rivers, and birds -
OL,8,Fmoving away from the bridges and
OL,9,Fmonuments currently featured.
OL,11,FThe consultation mirrors a similar
OL,12,Fmove by the UK, which earlier this
OL,13,Fyear asked the public which British
OL,14,Fwildlife they wanted to appear on Bank
OL,15,Fof England notes - replacing the
OL,16,Fhistorical figures who currently
OL,17,Foccupy them.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/33
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784913523
OL,3,CWhy euro notes are being redesigned -
OL,4,Cand how you can have a say
OL,6,FThe new European notes are not due to
OL,7,Fenter circulation for several years,
OL,8,Fso those with summer holidays planned
OL,9,Fin the EU this year still have a
OL,10,Fchance to see the current
OL,11,Farchitectural designs.
OL,13,FSo why is the EU changing the design,
OL,14,Fwhat might the new notes look like,
OL,15,Fand how can you get involved with
OL,16,Fchoosing the design?
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/33
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784913523
OL,3,CWhy euro notes are being redesigned -
OL,4,Cand how you can have a say
OL,6,FWhat are the designs being proposed?
OL,8,FMore than 1,000 designers initially
OL,9,Fsubmitted work, with various rounds of
OL,10,Fassessment eventually narrowing the
OL,11,Fselection down to the 10 designs
OL,12,Fcurrently being consulted on.
OL,14,FItaly had the highest amount of
OL,15,Finitial submissions, with the Czech
OL,16,FRepublic submitting the fewest.
OL,18,FDesigners had to stick to either of
OL,19,Fthe two themes, "European Culture:
OL,20,FShared Cultural Spaces", or "Rivers
OL,21,Fand Birds: Resilience in diversity".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/33
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
