PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784913523
OL,3,CWhy euro notes are being redesigned -
OL,4,Cand how you can have a say
OL,6,FThe ECB also stipulated exactly which
OL,7,Fcultural figures, birds, and rivers
OL,8,Fshould feature on each note.
OL,10,FFor European Culture:
OL,12,FAnd for Rivers and Birds:
OL,14,FBelow are the final shortlisted design
OL,15,Fsets with a short description of each
OL,16,Ffrom the ECB and designer.
OL,18,FDesign J - Ville Tietavainen
OL,26,@zD@VxpzD@Xxp
