OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784913523
OL,3,CWhy euro notes are being redesigned -
OL,4,Cand how you can have a say
OL,6,F"This euro banknote series tells a
OL,7,Fvisual story of European rivers, from
OL,8,Ftheir origins in mountain springs to
OL,9,Fmerging with the sea. The main
OL,10,Fcharacters are the European birds in
OL,11,Ftheir natural habitats. The higher the
OL,12,Fbanknote denomination, the closer the
OL,13,Fimagery gets to the sea. The security
OL,14,Ffoils each show one phase of a river
OL,15,Fwith the associated bird, and work as
OL,16,Fan infographic device, introducing the
OL,17,Fnarrative concept of the banknote
OL,18,Fseries. Even the EU buildings on the
OL,19,Freverse sides of the banknotes merge
OL,20,Fwith the wings of the particular birds
OL,21,Fon the front sides."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/33
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
