PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784913523
OL,3,CWhy euro notes are being redesigned -
OL,4,Cand how you can have a say
OL,6,F"From the beat of a bird's wing to the
OL,7,Fflow of rivers, movement is at the
OL,8,Fheart of this proposal. It seeks to
OL,9,Fembody both the dynamism of the EU and
OL,10,Fthe tangible and intangible flows that
OL,11,Fpass through its territory. As a true
OL,12,Fmessenger, the bird ` appearing alone
OL,13,Fon the front and as a group on the
OL,14,Fback ` symbolises the dialogue and
OL,15,Finterdependence between our societies
OL,16,Fand nature. From a river's source to
OL,17,Fthe ocean, the bird's flight reveals
OL,18,Fthe landscape it traverses through the
OL,19,Finterweaving of two patterns ` one
OL,20,Fhand-drawn in felt-tip pen and the
OL,21,Fother vector-based ` embodying
OL,22,Fcohesion through diversity."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/33
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
