OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784913523
OL,3,CWhy euro notes are being redesigned -
OL,4,Cand how you can have a say
OL,6,F"Water flows. It is the very
OL,7,Ffoundation for life, shaping our
OL,8,Fenvironment and the habitats for the
OL,9,Frich European birdlife depicted on the
OL,10,Fbanknotes. Also, water can take on
OL,11,Fmany characteristics, such as balance
OL,12,For consistency. Using these qualities
OL,13,Fas analogies for the EU institutions
OL,14,Fcreates trust and understanding of
OL,15,Ftheir functions. A drop might seem
OL,16,Fnegligible, but over centuries a
OL,17,Fstream is powerful enough to sculpt
OL,18,Fmountain ranges. One person might seem
OL,19,Finsignificant, but millions of people
OL,20,Funited by a common goal are resilient
OL,21,Fand powerful. In this light, water is
OL,22,Fa fitting analogy for the EU."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/33
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
