CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784913523
OL,3,CWhy euro notes are being redesigned -
OL,4,Cand how you can have a say
OL,6,F"The design aims to illustrate the
OL,7,Fofficial motto of the EU ` 'United in
OL,8,Fdiversity'. Europe is united by a rich
OL,9,Fshared cultural history and heritage,
OL,10,Frepresented by the portraits of iconic
OL,11,FEuropean figures. It is united by
OL,12,Fshared values and a sense of
OL,13,Fbelonging, strengthened by the
OL,14,Fdiversity of cultural identities. This
OL,15,Fdiversity is visualised in a collage
OL,16,Fthrough a multitude of forms and
OL,17,Ftextures that together create a new
OL,18,Fwhole, uniting these different
OL,19,Felements. The collage forms the
OL,20,Fbackground for the hand-drawn
OL,21,Fportraits and depictions of shared
OL,22,Fcultural spaces as concrete
OL,23,Fmanifestations of these ideas."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/33
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
