PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784913523
OL,3,CWhy euro notes are being redesigned -
OL,4,Cand how you can have a say
OL,6,FDesign E - Myrsini Vardopoulou
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/33
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30416
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784913523
OL,3,CWhy euro notes are being redesigned -
OL,4,Cand how you can have a say
OL,6,F"The communicative approach focuses on
OL,7,Fthe universal value of each person's
OL,8,Fwork rather than their personality.
OL,9,FThe circle and the symbols function as
OL,10,Fa visual message denoting an
OL,11,Fintellectual space. This space offers
OL,12,Fthe viewer immediate visual
OL,13,Ffamiliarity. Simultaneously, symbolic
OL,14,Fdetails provide subtle references for
OL,15,Fa deeper conceptual reading. In this
OL,16,Fway, the design communicates that,
OL,17,Fdespite the diversity of the
OL,18,Findividuals, their contribution
OL,19,Fconstitutes a unified source of
OL,20,Finspiration and a means of
OL,21,Freconnecting with familiar, yet ever-
OL,22,Fevolving cultural values."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/33
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
