OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784913523
OL,3,CWhy euro notes are being redesigned -
OL,4,Cand how you can have a say
OL,6,F"Six birds appear within abstracted
OL,7,Flandscapes, connected by the
OL,8,Fcontinuous journey of a river, from a
OL,9,Fmountain source to a stormy sea. Light
OL,10,Faccompanies this progression, evolving
OL,11,Ffrom a soft presence into a dynamic,
OL,12,Fincisive force with symbolic
OL,13,Fresonance. The scenes invite close
OL,14,Finspection, placing the viewer in the
OL,15,Fposition of a birdwatcher, gathering
OL,16,Ftraces of each species. On the
OL,17,Freverse, EU institutions are expressed
OL,18,Fthrough human gestures and a morphing
OL,19,Ffabric-like mesh. Hands hold,
OL,20,Fstabilise, align and debate,
OL,21,Fsuggesting cooperation in action,
OL,22,Fwhile light radiates from each
OL,23,Fbuilding across the EU territory."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/33
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
