PN,30428
SC,0028
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784913523
OL,3,CWhy euro notes are being redesigned -
OL,4,Cand how you can have a say
OL,6,FThe ECB also says the update will
OL,7,Fallow them to improve the anti-
OL,8,Fcounterfeiting measures incorporated
OL,9,Finto banknotes, as well as improve the
OL,10,Fenvironmental impact by refining the
OL,11,Fnotes' production methods.
OL,13,FThe current designs
OL,15,FThe designs currently in circulation
OL,16,Fwere introduced as updated versions of
OL,17,Fthe original euro notes between 2013
OL,18,Fand 2019.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G28/33
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
