OL,3,CWhy euro notes are being redesigned -
OL,4,Cand how you can have a say
OL,6,FThey are known as the Europa series,
OL,7,Fbecause two of the security features
OL,8,Fcontain a portrait of Princess Europa.
OL,10,FThis figure from Greek mythology
OL,11,Fprovides a visible link to the
OL,12,Fcontinent of Europe and also adds a
OL,13,Fhuman touch to the banknotes. One side
OL,14,Ffeatures an illustration of a
OL,15,Fdifferent bridge, and the other an
OL,16,Farch, door, or window.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G29/33
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
