PN,30430
SC,0030
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784913523
OL,3,CWhy euro notes are being redesigned -
OL,4,Cand how you can have a say
OL,6,FThe ECB says this design choice
OL,7,Freflects the "European spirit of
OL,8,Fopenness and cooperation", with the
OL,9,Freverse bridges representing
OL,10,F"communication between the people of
OL,11,FEurope and between Europe and the rest
OL,12,Fof the world".
OL,14,FThe designs are based on architectural
OL,15,Fstyles throughout various periods of
OL,16,FEurope's history, but do not show
OL,17,Factual existing monuments or bridges.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G30/33
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
