PN,30431
SC,0031
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784913523
OL,3,CWhy euro notes are being redesigned -
OL,4,Cand how you can have a say
OL,6,FThough the designs avoided showing
OL,7,Factual monuments to remain neutral,
OL,8,Fbetween 2011 and 2013, a public arts
OL,9,Fproject in the Dutch city of
OL,10,FSpijkenisse, saw real bridges built
OL,11,Facross canals mirroring the banknotes'
OL,12,Fdesigns.
OL,14,FThe concrete bridges were designed by
OL,15,FRobin Stam and completed in colours to
OL,16,Fmatch their corresponding notes.
OL,18,FHow can you get involved in choosing
OL,19,Fthe new designs?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G31/33
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
