OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784913523
OL,3,CWhy euro notes are being redesigned -
OL,4,Cand how you can have a say
OL,6,FAfter selecting the winning design
OL,7,Fsets from those submitted to the
OL,8,Fpublic callout, the ECB has invited
OL,9,Fthe public to submit their thoughts on
OL,10,Fthe different sets.
OL,12,FUsing the link below, you can select
OL,13,Ffrom a series of options how much you
OL,14,Flike each set of designs.
OL,16,FYou can also select up to three
OL,17,Freasons from a set list of why you
OL,18,Ffeel the way you do about each set.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G32/33
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
