OL,3,CWhy euro notes are being redesigned -
OL,4,Cand how you can have a say
OL,6,FFollow this link to have your say
OL,7,Fabout the euro's future design, with
OL,8,Fthe final selection being made around
OL,9,Fthe end of the year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G33/33
